graph TD
  Start([Start / Landing Page]) --> PublicActions[Public Actions]
  PublicActions --> |User Login/Register| UserAuth
  PublicActions --> |Guest Emergency| GuestEmergency
  PublicActions --> |Beneficiary Request| BeneficiaryRequest

  subgraph UserFlow [User]
    UserAuth --> UserLogin[User Login]
    UserLogin --> UserDashboard[User Dashboard]
    UserDashboard --> ManageAccounts[Manage Social Accounts]
    ManageAccounts --> ConnectPlatform[Connect/Refresh Tokens]
    UserDashboard --> Alerts[Alerts & Settings]
  end

  subgraph BeneficiaryFlow [Beneficiary]
    BeneficiaryRequest --> BeneficiaryForm[Submit Beneficiary Request]
    BeneficiaryForm --> PDFUpload{Optional PDF Upload}
    PDFUpload -->|Yes| SavePDF[Save PDF to /static/uploads/beneficiary_docs]
    PDFUpload -->|No| SaveNoPDF[Save without document]
    SavePDF --> SaveReq[Request Saved (status: pending)]
    SaveNoPDF --> SaveReq
    SaveReq --> NotifyAdmins[Notify Admins (email/notification)]
    SaveReq --> AdminReview

    AdminReview -->|Approve| ApproveAction[Mark request approved]
    AdminReview -->|Reject| RejectAction[Mark request rejected]

    ApproveAction --> NotifyBeneficiaryApproved[Notify beneficiary: approved]
    RejectAction --> NotifyBeneficiaryRejected[Notify beneficiary: rejected]

    ApprovedLogin[Beneficiary Login attempt]
    ApprovedLogin --> CheckStatus{status?}
    CheckStatus -->|pending| PendingMsg[Show: "Your emergency access account is pending"]
    CheckStatus -->|rejected| RejectedMsg[Show: "Your request was not accepted"]
    CheckStatus -->|approved| LoginSuccess[Login -> Beneficiary Dashboard]

    LoginSuccess --> ViewApprovedAccounts[View approved social accounts (PIN-protected)]
  end

  subgraph AdminFlow [Admin]
    AdminLogin[Admin Login] --> AdminDashboard[Admin Dashboard]
    AdminDashboard --> ReviewEmergencies[Review Emergency Requests]
    ReviewEmergencies --> ViewPDF[View / Download uploaded PDF]
    ReviewEmergencies --> ApproveBtn[Approve Request]
    ReviewEmergencies --> RejectBtn[Reject Request]
    AdminDashboard --> GenerateReport[Generate Emergency Report (PDF)]
    AdminDashboard --> ManageTokens[Activate / Deactivate Emergency Tokens]
  end

  GuestEmergency --> GuestForm[Submit Guest Emergency Request]
  GuestForm --> GuestNotify[Notify Admins]
  GuestNotify --> AdminReview
  AdminReview --> ManageTokens

  AdminReview --> AdminDashboard
  NotifyAdmins --> AdminDashboard
  NotifyBeneficiaryApproved --> BeneficiaryLogin[Beneficiary notified]
  NotifyBeneficiaryRejected --> BeneficiaryLogin

  Start --> PublicActions
